moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658eb89c5dbe36496dbc2195fc27ac00ad8973a5","tid":410270,"uid":4284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問下 用ipad頭同尿袋叉係咪無咁好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順便一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁用靚尿袋同cheap雞尿袋既分別同火牛係咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尿袋係咪好易叉到燒底板"},{"pid":"c959270ee0486fbce4b000ead1f01749e2e83c0b","tid":410270,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"推到啲行家入黎答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08130f114a0db0a0c1b2cd351d50b9d7c3d08c7f","tid":410270,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好用快差牛<br />\n愈慢粒電壽命愈長</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df162b9a02bf02095eed23e3c806db0e4f74c182","tid":410270,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢種穩唔穩陣？<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.mobilefun.co.uk/graphics/productgalleries/47946/a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.mobilefun.co.uk%2Fgraphics%2Fproductgalleries%2F47946%2Fa.jpg&h=d1f98904&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用嗰隻寫話有smart IC識自動調節<br />\n有啲新款仲有quick charge"},{"pid":"7f12503a4ba964bded8fb604b5b8818521dc342d","tid":410270,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢種穩唔穩陣？<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.mobilefun.co.uk/graphics/productgalleries/47946/a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.mobilefun.co.uk%2Fgraphics%2Fproductgalleries%2F47946%2Fa.jpg&h=d1f98904&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用嗰隻寫話有smart IC識自動調節<br />\n有啲新款仲有quick charge</blockquote><br />\n大佬點睇呀<br />\n要睇電流電壓交流直流穩定性大把野要睇<br />\n目測咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是Q但啦"},{"pid":"e01503d646e6b14e2793e24cd2f4457dfda073b6","tid":410270,"uid":76247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"用緊anker 線 apple 火牛 有朋友試過用街邊線 後尾要去蘋果換電 天才話原來叉到個電池發脹左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9302d98249f1f284a428a1d388d166c64b239ac4","tid":410270,"uid":78492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:02:55.000Z","msg":"其實講緊咩線？<br />\nIphone 同an機<br />\n揀線可以好唔同<br />\niPhone 有d線$50,有d$100（差唔多長度）<br />\n係因為mfi認證<br />\nGoogle下mfi就知個充電頭有塊認證晶片去控制電流同截電<br />\n無認證既線，當iOS 升級左一兩代就會充唔入電<br />\n同無截電呢個功能（充滿電唔識轉絹流充電）<br />\n<br />\n至於火牛<br />\n影響電池安全既係電壓，電流大細其實無咩關係<br />\n所以用0.5a同用2.4a牛差電，分別只在快同慢<br />\n但重點係電壓要控制得好，電壓控制唔好就好易出事（呢個亦係尿袋點解有d咁貴既原因之一，靚尿袋有粒靚ic識截電同變壓）<br />\n<br />\n用電腦機箱usb差既問題係電壓過低/電流細，虧住咁差，長遠影響就係舊電電容量變細（因為長期差唔盡）慢慢就虧。<br />\n所以用細電流低電壓去喂係錯誤觀念。"},{"pid":"8bc55c88907931bb0442eb5f4cab0c1bdc9ec20b","tid":410270,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"插電腦叉電又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0ac69b700581bc7fab14de9f2aef14f8f529c4","tid":410270,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>插電腦叉電又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得0.3A At least 叉十個鐘. 粒電應該好撚襟用"},{"pid":"d2bef0436a6b79ac09873fcfe58ff3fe052f2974","tid":410270,"uid":4284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實講緊咩線？<br />\nIphone 同an機<br />\n揀線可以好唔同<br />\niPhone 有d線$50,有d$100（差唔多長度）<br />\n係因為mfi認證<br />\nGoogle下mfi就知個充電頭有塊認證晶片去控制電流同截電<br />\n無認證既線，當iOS 升級左一兩代就會充唔入電<br />\n同無截電呢個功能（充滿電唔識轉絹流充電）<br />\n<br />\n至於火牛<br />\n影響電池安全既係電壓，電流大細其實無咩關係<br />\n所以用0.5a同用2.4a牛差電，分別只在快同慢<br />\n但重點係電壓要控制得好，電壓控制唔好就好易出事（呢個亦係尿袋點解有d咁貴既原因之一，靚尿袋有粒靚ic識截電同變壓）<br />\n<br />\n用電腦機箱usb差既問題係電壓過低/電流細，虧住咁差，長遠影響就係舊電電容量變細（因為長期差唔盡）慢慢就虧。<br />\n所以用細電流低電壓去喂係錯誤觀念。</blockquote><br />\n電流過大好似會燒底板？"}]}